author: @zayjanin2733
text: I stopped stanning kpop groups since the disbandment of Wanna One. I just casually listen to different kpop groups' songs but not really being their fan. And then recently I stumbled to this group called Seventeen from watching Game Caterers Hybe Edition.  Boo Seungkwan really caught my attention because of his silliness so I decided to research about them and watch their old videos. Upon watching them in just a few days, I was amazed how good and genuine their relationship was and also the talents they have; dancing, singing, producing their own songs and choreography, and their own shows. Watching their old videos feels like I have known them for years. This group lighted my dead heart for kpop that's dead since the disbandment of my fave. I am now ready to embrace this diamond life and will treasure them. Thank you for being my escape recently, thank you for saving me, Seventeen. 💎🫶
